Samsung Galaxy M01 Benchmark Scores Overview

Samsung Galaxy M01 is powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 439. The processor is Octa core (2 GHz, Quad core, Cortex A53 + 1.45 GHz, Quad core, Cortex A53) that uses 64 bit architecture and Adreno 505 GPU. It runs on Android v10 (Q) operating system with 3 GB RAM and 32 GB ROM.

Samsung Galaxy M01 AnTuTu Score:

Samsung Galaxy M01 has an overall AnTuTu score of 103,806. The benchmark app also gives individual scores for CPU, Memory, GPU, and UX tests. Samsung Galaxy M01 scored 38,873 for CPU, 32,606 for Memory, 10,670 for GPU, and 22,491 for UX test.
